data.description: Located in Hay Creek Sub,this 2,634-sf home has plenty of space & is perfect for entertaining family & friends. Lg family rm w/a fireplace. The kitchen has an eating area, island, work station & coffee station. Separate dining rm & living rm adds add'l space for entertaining. Working from home? Office space is ready. Laundry & half bath complete the main floor. Upstairs are 3 bedrms, full bathrm & a Primary Suite w/cathedral ceilings, lg bath w/a soaking tub,dual sinks,shower & 2 walk in-closets. Need more space, full basement is a blank slate & waiting to be finished. Outside is .47 acres w/a lg stamp concrete patio,mature trees & backs to the community walking path. Lakes, State Parks & Lakeland trail are just minutes away.  Easy commute to Ann Arbor.
